text:
Hey Paulina,
Thank you for reaching out, I’m so sorry I haven't been in touch; I’m having a nightmare trying to sort out the electric/boiler and internet at my new house and I just haven't had enough time to sit down to chat! Almost all sorted now though :raised_hands::zap:
How is second year going so far? I’d love to see the updates on your monkey sculpt! Is it going okay working in a team?

I wanted to say as well that your deer is looking really great, nice job! Is the Skyblivion project something you can make some money out of? It would be great to put that on your CV too either way :deer:
